{"tid":1002871,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【負資產重現】去年第四季錄262宗負資產 兩年來首見","createTime":"2019-01-31T08:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T15:13:16.000Z","uid":26418,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4bb828a36bc7fec7e538ad0019d77d9f01abaa","tid":1002871,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:52:06.000Z","msg":"金管局今日公布負資產住宅按揭貸款的最新調查結果。2018年第4季的負資產住宅按揭貸款宗數為262宗，是自從2016年第4季以來再次錄得負資產個案。金管局指，這些個案涉及銀行職員的住屋按揭貸款或按揭保險計劃的貸款，而這類貸款的按揭成數一般較高。<br />\n<br />\n金額方面，2018年第4季的負資產住宅按揭貸款所涉及的金額為11.89億元。負資產住宅按揭貸款中無抵押部分的金額為5,800萬元。銀行自從2011年第1季起，並無錄得任何拖欠3個月以上的負資產住宅按揭貸款紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n香港過去曾出現大量負資產個案，1997年金融風暴之後，樓價一直下跌了六年至2003年沙士時期，累積跌幅超過六成，故於1997年後幾年開始湧現負資產個案，至2003年達到負資產高峰期，當時負資產宗數超過十萬宗，佔供樓人士比例超過兩成，所以成為社會一個民生問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190131&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59208167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190131%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59208167&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6jQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=6c67cd82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190131%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59208167&h=f660277a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190131&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59208167</a>"},{"pid":"fbb3aa76d717e18f7b6fcae43841c0e756b011ec","tid":1002871,"uid":162526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"我朋友上年440萬摸頂買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4dbfccddf6ea23e2ac63f2ee43f5ee15f25bba","tid":1002871,"uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"一定要推返上去"},{"pid":"db5c3da8b6b750a9dfdd6cf9bf36643ad5f10f2d","tid":1002871,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:02:55.000Z","msg":"負資產都算係資產呀"},{"pid":"10694c44564f1ad63944a5389562c238b67912ad","tid":1002871,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59faecb5db439451653e0b9c7ea1e9d77162df2b","tid":1002871,"uid":76745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:17:58.000Z","msg":"冇資產有咩資格笑負資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25088f9eac5128db771403e3ea4d5b3353440aa9","tid":1002871,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"陷阱型住家用資產"},{"pid":"15abb5abd9b99795782c5d45797a45072aac351a","tid":1002871,"uid":57848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"冇事啦升返啦，唔計"},{"pid":"eb776c007186c657b31d220c120eab6bc3222e33","tid":1002871,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59faecb5db439451653e0b9c7ea1e9d77162df2b","tid":1002871,"uid":76745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:17:58.000Z","msg":"冇資產有咩資格笑負資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:13:16.000Z","msg":"無產階級革命份子無資格笑人負資產"}]}